data.description: Wonderful well cared for home in Whispering Pines. This home features large oversized lot, formal dining, large kitchen island, first floor guest suite, enormous bonus that can be used as a 5th bedroom and whole house water filtration system. Backyard features a fire pit and 14x14' pergola and covered patio. Fireplace has gas logs, but no tank is in place. Now offering $10,000 seller credit for closing costs, rate buy down or paint credit with acceptable offer.
